0.2
	o Added script for NaturalDocs(http://www.naturaldocs.org/) 
	  (doc/gendoc.sh)
	  [ Thu Aug 26 23:26:25 JST 2004 ]

	o Added "rockenfield" the fltk + OpenGL frame buffer driver
	  (tools/fltkview/)
	  [ Thu Aug 26 23:15:23 JST 2004 ]

	o Support for OpenEXR image file format display driver.
	o Experimental implementation of Metropolis Light Transport
          (metropolis.c)
	o Show display drivers available when -info option is specified.
	o Experimental RenderMan shadeding language support.
	o Supports Subdivision surface(SubdivisionMesh, "catmull-clark" scheme)
	o Supports quad polygon(PointsPolygons, PointsGeneralPolygons)
	o Added 2D Fibonacci lattice points generator(qmc.c).

0.1.3
	o Added Faure's permutation method(qmc.c)
	o Added generalized van der Corput sequence(qmc.c)
	o Displays elapsed time left(ETA) of rendering.
	o Displays persentage(%) for rendering.
	o Added support of ReadArchive.

0.1.2 or lower
	o A lot of trivial changes...

